# One proxy URL per line. Supports http, https, socks5.
# Lines starting with # are ignored. Blank lines are skipped.
#
# Examples:
# http://user:pass@residential-proxy1:8080
# http://user:pass@residential-proxy2:8080
# socks5://user:pass@socks-proxy:1080
#
# Tip: Use residential proxies for Twitter scraping.
# Datacenter proxies are easily detected and blocked.
